Well, I mean...

1:08:41.192 --> 1:08:44.026
She had a breakdown.
You know, a mental one.

1:08:44.179 --> 1:08:45.845
Mm-hmm.

1:08:45.864 --> 1:08:48.197
- While you were...
- I was sleeping.

1:08:48.350 --> 1:08:51.292
